Auto Translator Extension
Copyright © 2024 Hoài Nghĩa - Cafe Nhớ

Author: Hoài Nghĩa - Cafe Nhớ
Email: hoainghia22@gmail.com
Telegram: @hoainghia22
GitHub: https://github.com/hoainghia22
Website: https://cafenho.net

This Chrome extension provides intelligent text translation functionality
using Google Gemini AI and OpenAI GPT APIs. It supports multiple languages
and offers both manual and automatic translation features.

Features:
- Multi-language support (English, French, Spanish, German, Chinese, Japanese, Korean)
- Dual API support (Gemini AI and OpenAI GPT)
- Customizable keyboard shortcuts
- Auto-translation for input fields
- Modern, responsive UI design
- Secure API key storage

For more information, visit: https://github.com/hoainghia22/auto-translator-extension
